These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
City: paris, prague, boston, berlin
1. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person traveling to paris##6
3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person traveling to paris is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | berlin | paris | boston | prague |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, van, bus, subway
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
4. the person driving the van is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | van  | bus    | taxi | subway    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, swisher, dunhill, old-henry
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the old-henry-smoker is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the dunhill-smoker##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
4. the doctor is the siglo-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the siglo-smoker is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | old-henry       | swisher  | siglo  | dunhill |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

