.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, grapes, apricot, pumpkin
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person eating apricot is the person eating apricot##1
6. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
8. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | grapes | apricot    | apple  | pumpkin   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

