.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, western, superhero
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, photographer, social-worker
1. the coach is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
7. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5
8. the person watching horror movies is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | horror  | adventure        | western      | superhero          |
| Job        | coach | journalist | social-worker | photographer |

