.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, snake
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
3. the fan indie is not the owner of the mouse##6
4. the owner of the lizard is between the fan pop and the owner of the mouse##2
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the owner of the chinchilla##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | mouse | lizard    | chinchilla | snake |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

