.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, blueberry, cucumber, grapes
City: marseilles, new-york, venice, nizza
1. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
2. the person eating grapes is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
3. the person traveling to new-york is the person eating grapes##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person traveling to venice is not the person eating grapes##6
6. the person eating blueberry is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
7. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
8. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | asparagus  | cucumber | blueberry | grapes |
| Transport   | venice | marseilles     | nizza     | new-york    |

