.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, banana, lettuce, pomegranate
4 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, snooker, billiard
1. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
2. the person eating banana is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
3. the person eating asparagus is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
5. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating banana and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the person eating banana is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate | banana      | asparagus | lettuce   |
| Movie-Genre   | mah-jongg     | snooker | billiard   | monopoly |

