.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-14::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, bridge, billiard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, mystery, superhero
1. the person watching mystery movies is not the person playing billiard##6
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is between the person playing bridge and the person playing backgammon##2
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | billiard       | backgammon | mah-jongg     | bridge     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery       | superhero | martial-arts |

