.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, journalist, mechanic, paramedic
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, ebony, chestnut
1. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
3. the person who likes blood-red is not the analyst##6
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes ebony is between the journalist and the person who likes blood-red##2
6. the journalist is not the person who likes yellow##6
7. the paramedic is on the right of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | analyst  | mechanic | paramedic | journalist |
| Sport   | yellow | blood-red | ebony   | chestnut |

