2. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
3. the fan soul is on the left of the fan funk##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
5. the fan classical is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the subway is not the fan pop##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | soul | funk | pop | classical |
| Transport   | roller   | bike       | jet-ski    | subway     |

