.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice
There 4 different types of food: orange, spinach, mango, grapefruit
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating orange##1
2. the person drinking fanta is not the person eating spinach##6
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating mango##1
7. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | juice    | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | fanta         |
| Sport      | spinach | mango | orange          | grapefruit |

