.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, snooker, mah-jongg
1. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
2. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |
| Pet     | snooker  | whist      | scrabble  | mah-jongg       |

