.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, mirinda, water
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, snooker, go
1. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing whist is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
6. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | go  | bridge   | snooker | whist |

 